WEBVTT

00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:03.000
Go to the Collection's Authorization tab

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:09.000
Configure the Authorization type

00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:16.000
Create an Environment Variable for your credentials

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Set the Variable as secret so the value is masked on the screen

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:26.000
Ensure that your request is set to Inherit auth from parent (i.e. Collection)

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:30.000
Click Send to test your credentials
